GetStringValue

public static java.lang.String GetStringValue(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode entry,
                                              java.lang.String key,
                                              java.lang.String default_value,
                                              boolean shortcut)
Get string from object flavor of JsonNode.

If the specified field key of the non-null JsonNode entry object is textual, then that value is returned. Also, if shortcut is true and the entry is textual, the textual value is returned. In both cases, the resulting text will be trimmed of leading and trailing whitespace and must not be empty. Otherwise, the default_value is returned.

Parameters:
entry - the source of the string
key - the field name when entry is an object.
default_value - the value to return when a value can not be fetched
shortcut - enables/disables shortcut if entry is textual

Get boolean from object flavor of JsonNode.

If the specified field key of the non-null JsonNode entry object is boolean, then that value is returned. If the field is textual and represents a parseable boolean string, then that value is returned. Otherwise, the default_value is returned.

Parameters:
entry - the source of the boolean
key - the field name when entry is an object.
default_value - the value to return when a value can not be fetched

ToValuePB

public static org.openflow.northboundapi.proto.ValuesPB.ValuePB.Builder ToValuePB(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode root,
                                                                                  org.openflow.northboundapi.proto.ValuesPB.ValuePB.Builder ret_val)
Converts a JsonNode into a ValuePB builder.

Converts an int, long, boolean, textual, binary, array, or object JsonNode into a corresponding ValuePB builder element, recursively descending down non-terminal JsonNode elements to build out the matching ValuePB hierarchy.

AddDictEntry

public static void AddDictEntry(java.lang.String name,
                                com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode value,
                                org.openflow.northboundapi.proto.ValuesPB.ValuePB.Builder dict)
Adds a name-value entry to the "dict" field of a ValuePB element.

Creates a new "dict" (repeatable) field element of the specified ValuePB builder element and sets the "name" portion of the "dict" entry to the specified name string and the "value" portion of the "dict" entry to a ToValuePB() conversion of the specifed JsaonNode value.
